title: Stoner Cats 1% Charity Contribution
body:
As promised, 1% of minting revenue and 1% of secondary revenue from "Stoner Cats" is committed to going to a charity that deals with Alzheimer's and aging.
We'd like to have you as "Stoner Cats" owners make our first community-powered choice. 
Nothing can go off the rails here, but maybe you have an opinion on one or versus the other or want to do some research.
Let's test our collaborative decision-making and do some good.
author: 0x53Df7C1a39248589013c3bDa3D0d1cC9fAB1651C
